{"tid":2245619,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"跳閘男襲休班警罪成 還柙候判","createTime":"2020-10-16T11:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T17:43:41.000Z","uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"03b9d8041215c30f92410e908b9549aed2e41be9","tid":2245619,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:04:08.000Z","msg":"港鐵男乘客去年在鰂魚涌站跳閘，遭正準備前往上班的休班警逮個正著。乘客其後補票出閘，惟休班警窮追不捨，從後擒抱，兩人倒地糾纏，混亂間休班警左眼受傷。男乘客被控襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，經審訊後今被裁定罪成。裁判官崔美霞先為被告索取背景報告，並下令將他還柙至本月29日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n至於休班警受初時自言遇襲兩至三下，書面口供則說幾下，未能提供實際次數，崔官認為沒有抵觸或不合理之處。當時警員下身被壓，瞬間被打眼幾次，情況混亂，沒有看清被告襲擊動作，不足為奇。崔官認為休班警是誠實可靠證人。"},{"pid":"88bb65a9ce83f6cefdd9a82b5fe765ae917b94e6","tid":2245619,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:04:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/UTGVEDRQ4FE7BGK54DB5TNVZLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FUTGVEDRQ4FE7BGK54DB5TNVZLU%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVUwvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=f32fe605\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FUTGVEDRQ4FE7BGK54DB5TNVZLU%2F&h=112650e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/UTGVEDRQ4FE7BGK54DB5TNVZLU/</a>"},{"pid":"3dbfe16ff0821be4835dfb9c9209a7ce9b1c9a7f","tid":2245619,"uid":39503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2db71d50b8baca6ba6d58c9067244c5f972a958","tid":2245619,"uid":86673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:09:00.000Z","msg":"誠實可靠？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929b20d390c9824264cdd09fceb4ec